Package: bkcde
Imports: parallel, pbmcapply, stats, MCPAN
Suggests: lpcde, progress
Type: Package
Title: Boundary Corrected Polynomial Adaptive Kernel Conditional Density Estimation
Version: 1.7
Date: 2024-08-02
Author: Jeffrey S. Racine
Maintainer: Jeffrey S. Racine <raicnej@mcmaster.ca>
Description: This package uses data-driven methods to jointly determine bandwidths, the polynomial order, and approximates unknown bounds freeing the user from having to select any of these in applied settings.
License: GPL (>= 3)
